\is1 Study Notes
\ili1 1. What texts do you consider the best for proving that the Scriptures teach us that we must know we are children of God?
\ili1 2. What are the three points in which the sucking child is to us an example of the young child in Christ in his dealing with the Word?
\ili1 3. What must the young Christian do when he has little blessing in the reading of God’s Word? He must set himself down through faith in fellowship with Jesus Himself and believe that Jesus will teach him through the Spirit, and so trustfully continue in the reading.
