\ili1 1. What is the distinction between the covering of sin by God and by man? How does man do it? How does God do it?
\ili1 2. What are the great hindrances in the way of the confession of sin?
\ili2 • Ignorance about sin,
\ili2 • Fear to come with sin to the Holy Father,
\ili2 • The endeavour to come to God with something good,
\ili2 • Unbelief in the power of the blood of Jesus and in the riches of grace.
