\im 2) Matthew 4:1; Matthew 4:10
\im 3) Matthew 12:28; Mark 4:15; Luke 13:16; Acts 10:38
\im 4) Matthew 16:23; Luke 22:31–32
\im 5) Luke 10:18; Luke 22:3; Luke 22:53; John 12:31; John 14:30; John 16:11; Romans 16:20; Colossians 2:15; 2 Thessalonians 2:8–9; 1 John 3:8
\im 6) 1 Corinthians 7:5; 2 Corinthians 2:10–11
