\im 6) Exodus 10:23; 2 Samuel 23:4; Psalm 36:10; Isaiah 60:1; Isaiah 60:20; 1 John 1:5; 4:16
\im 7) Josh 7:13; Isaiah 58:10; Isaiah 59:1–2; Isaiah 59:9; Matthew 15:14–16; 2 Corinthians 6:14; Ephesians 5:8; Ephesians 5:14; 1 Thessalonians 5:5; 1 John 2:10
\im 8) John 12:36; 11:40; Romans 15:13; 1 Peter 1:3
