\im 6) 1 Corinthians 8:13; 1 Corinthians 9:25–27; 1 Corinthians 10:23; 2 Corinthians 6:16–17; 2 Timothy 2:4
\im 7) Genesis 22:13; Genesis 22:17; 2 Chronicles 25:9; Luke 18:29–30; John 12:24–25; Philippians 3:8
