\im 2) John 8:32; Galatians 4:21; Galatians 4:31; Galatians 5:1
\im 3) John 8:34; Romans 7:14; Romans 7:23; 2 Peter 2:19
\im 4) Romans 5:21; Romans 6:13–14
\im 5) Romans 4:15; Romans 5:13; Romans 5:20; Romans 7:13
